                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-1262" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES KIRBY</persName>
                  </hi>.(<hi rend="italic">police-constable R</hi> 186.) I took the prisoner, and received these two half-crowns from Mr. Worth.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
